summary: This file replaces the 2nd preset for female Khajiit.
descriptionHtml:
This is a preset I made of my female Khajiit character Ajira. I really like how she turned out and figured it might interest others as well.

Installation: Just drop the \"Ajira Preset.esp\" in the Skyrim/Data folder.

Recommended textures: \"CoverKhajiit\" by Mr.Lenski -> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/5941//? and 
\"More accurate Khajiit chin and lips paint\" by RainKitty -> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6956//?
author: bokloes
